<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Roberto Castro</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="site-wrapper">
            <h1><a href="/">Roberto Castro</a></h1>
            <nav>
                <a href="/">Home</a>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main>
        <div class="site-wrapper">
            <section class="home-bio">
                <h2>Hey, I'm Rob 👋</h2>
                <p>Software engineer and entrepreneur from Costa Rica 🇨🇷 who loves building simple, powerful tools. I code in Java and Rust, and care deeply about clean design and clever ideas.</p>
                <div class="social-links">
                    <a href="https://github.com/castrovroberto" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
                    <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/roberto-castro-valenzuela-b428a731/" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a>
                    <a href="https://twitter.com/rubeite" target="_blank">Twitter</a>
                    <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@rubeite" target="_blank">YouTube</a>
                    <a href="mailto:castro.roberto@pm.me">Email</a>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="posts-section">
                <h3>Writing</h3>
                <ul class="post-list">
                    {% for post in collections.posts | reverse %}
                        <li>
                            <a href="{{ post.url }}">
                                <span class="post-title">{{ post.data.title }}</span>
                                <span class="post-date">{{ post.date | readableDate("MMM d, yyyy") }}</span>
                            </a>
                        </li>
                    {% endfor %}
                </ul>
            </section>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <div class="site-wrapper">
            <p>&copy; 2025 Roberto Castro</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
